continuing charging the selected cell at the charging current if the measured voltage is not greater than the voltage set-point;
determining if the charging current was at a minimum charging current if the voltage of the selected cell is greater than the voltage set-point;
reducing the charging current for the selected cell by a predetermined amount if the charging current was not at the minimum charging current if the measured voltage of the selected cell is greater than the voltage set-point.

